{
  "texts": [
    "To supplement these studies, we analyzed the content produced by humans and GPT-4 to examine semantic differences-specifically, the semantic relationship of the reappraisals to their vignettes, linguistic complexity, and characteristic reappraisal vocabulary.",
    "The goal of this study was to compare the quality of reappraisals between humans and GPT in Vignettes.",
    "We preregistered only exploratory hypotheses for this investigation (https://osf.io/3c4tj).",
    "We received IRB approval (IRB23-0216) prior to conducting the task.",
    "We had two sets of participants for Study 1, participants who produced reappraisals (reappraisers) and those who rated the quality of reappraisal (raters)."
  ]
}